Package: CocktailDBR
Type: Package
Title: CocktailDBR allows user to pull cocktail info from TheCocktailDB API and 
       search for cocktails based on certain criterias
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Authors@R: person("Yuhua", "Ding", email = "yd2511@columbia.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yd2511@columbia.edu>
Description: TheCocktailDB API does not require API key to access.
             CocktailDBR allows user to download a complete list of cocktails listed
             on TheCocktailDB API as well as detailed instructions and ingredients.
             This package also provides a local data.frame contains the latest list of
             cocktails from pulled from the API to save time for users. There are several
             API endpoints require Patreon support to access, please check API website
             thecocktaildb.com/api.php for more detail. 
URL:  https://github.com/yuhuading/ydcolumbia/tree/master/CocktailDBR 
BugReports: https://github.com/yuhuading/ydcolumbia/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    httr,
    stringr,
    jsonlite,
    dplyr,
    tidyr
Suggests: 
